e) Proposals to Change Splits (DAO-style)

Route: /dashboard/owner/proposals

To change percentages fairly (so owner canâ€™t just rug team), we use voting.

Flow:

Owner clicks â€œCreate split change proposalâ€

Selects team + new percentages

Contract function:

