But for hackathon, you can skip this and just read from contracts.

ğŸŒŠ Complete Flow Summary
When setting up a new team:

Owner connects wallet â†’ /dashboard/owner

Clicks Create Team â†’ createTeam()

Adds members + percentages â†’ addMember()

Team is now ready to receive payments.

